And when testing test against the actual values.
    test:assertEquals(outputs[0], "John Doe");
    test:assertEquals(outputs[1], 50); // `50` instead of `"50"`
If there are time constraints, I guess we can go ahead with these changes for the time-being. But let's create an issue to track improving these. WDYT?

